<p class="text-neutral-700">Click <strong class="font-medium">Test</strong> on the Contact Group to fire a synthetic Down alert.</p>

<p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">Or fire one by hand with curl:</p>

<pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-sm bg-neutral-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-neutral-900">curl -X POST "<%= public_webhook_url(parser_type: source.parser_type, token: source.token) %>" -d "Status=Down&URL=https://pingrb.com&Name=pingrb.com&StatusCode=503"</pre>
